page.title: 10Housing
page.content: This is a list of housing available in our D Block.1.Bungalow.2.Semi_detached houses.3.Detached houses.4.Terraced houses.5.Flats.6.Maisonetts.7.Council houses.8.Sheltered housing.My house is a detached house.It is not joined on to another house.A semi_detached house is built on to another house.Terraced houses are built in rows all joined to each other.Flats are apartments inside buildings which may contain many many flats.All rooms are on one floor.Maisonetts are like flatsbut teir rooms are on two floors.Council houses can be terracedor semi_detached they are not privately owned but are owned by the public though the councils.Sheltered housing is mainly for the elderly or the handicapped. They live in a community with a warden to help in time of trouble.Bungalows have no upstairs room.....
